 and compared with empirical evidence with the aim to either stress their importance or to debunk them as myths. The final part looks into the implications and possibilities for policy making.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aTerrorismxPrevention. 0aTerrorism. 4aConflict and Peace. 4aPolitics and Government. 4aSocial and Political Sciences. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / General.2bisacsh  aTerrorism, Counterterrorism, Policy-making, Terrorism Studies.1 aRoy van Zuijdewijn, Jeanine, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAmsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2022z978311076709408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2z978311076700108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishz978311099389908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Political Science 2022 Englishz978311099451308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Political Science 2022z9783110994407oZDB-23-PLW40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9789400604353?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9789400604353423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9789400604353/original  a978-3-11-076700-1  DG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2b2022  a978-3-11-076709-4  Amsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2022b2022  a978-3-11-099389-9  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishb2022  a978-3-11-099451-3  EBOOK PACKAGE Political Science 2022 Englishb2022  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_SN  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  